hopobject.body: I'm only getting an answering machine mopharma digital solutions Mix your tipples with travel at this quirky event, which sees a "captain" from Vestal Vodka welcome you onboard a 50ft canal boat for a cruise. You'll sail along Regent's Canal and pass through the canal network's longest tunnel, before ending up in Islington - all the while enjoying a clutch of vodka-themed cocktails. Drunken attempts to wrest control of the steering wheel presumably not encouraged.
